        Dcl-F CZGD02A0 Usage(*Input) Keyed INCLUDE(CZTD02A2) PREFIX(D20:3);
        Dcl-F cmgq08a0 Usage(*Input) Keyed ignore(cmtq08a1:cmtq08a3);
        Dcl-F SSG043A0 Usage(*Input) Keyed RENAME(SSH04310:SSH04310A);


        //Field Definitions.

        Dcl-S Count        Zoned(4:0);
        Dcl-S Format       Char(8);
        Dcl-S GenLen       Char(8);
        Dcl-S InLibrary    Char(10);
        Dcl-S InType       Char(10);
        Dcl-S ObjectLib    Char(20);
        Dcl-S SpaceVal     Char(1)    inz(*BLANKS);
        Dcl-S SpaceAuth    Char(10)   inz('*CHANGE');
        Dcl-S SpaceText    Char(50)   inz(*BLANKS);
        Dcl-S SpaceRepl    Char(10)   inz('*YES');
        Dcl-S SpaceAttr    Char(10)   inz(*BLANKS);
        Dcl-S UserSpaceOut Char(20);
        Dcl-S Worktype     Char(10)   inz('*OUTQ');


        Dcl-DS *N;
          StartPosit     Bindec(4)  Pos(1);
          StartLen       Bindec(4)  Pos(5);
          SpaceLen       Bindec(4)  Pos(9);
          ReceiveLen     Bindec(4)  Pos(13);
          MessageKey     Bindec(4)  Pos(17);
          MsgDtaLen      Bindec(4)  Pos(21);
          MsgQueNbr      Bindec(4)  Pos(25);
        End-DS;

        //-- Retrieve object description:  -------------------------------
        Dcl-PR RtvObjD  ExtPgm( 'QUSROBJD' );
          RoRcvVar       Char(32767) Options( *VarSize );
          RoRcvVarLen    Int(10)    Const;
          RoFmtNam       Char(8)    Const;
          RoObjNamQ      Char(20)   Const;
          RoObjTyp       Char(10)   Const;
          RoError        Char(32767) Options( *VarSize );
        End-PR;


        //Date structure for retriving userspace info

        Dcl-DS InputDs;
          UserSpace      Char(20)   Pos(1);
          SpaceName      Char(10)   Pos(1);
          SpaceLib       Char(10)   Pos(11);
          InpFileLib     Char(20)   Pos(29);
          InpFFilNam     Char(10)   Pos(29);
          InpFFilLib     Char(10)   Pos(39);
          InpRcdFmt      Char(10)   Pos(49);
        End-DS;

0.00    Dcl-S DATE0        Date; //     130124
2.00    Dcl-S DATE1        Date; //     130129
0.00    Dcl-S DATE2        Date       DATFMT(*JIS); //     130129
4.00    Dcl-S DATE3        Date       INZ(D'2001-01-12'); //     130129
5.00    Dcl-S DATE3_CHAR   Char(10); //     130129
0.00    Dcl-S len          Int(5); //     130130
6.00    Dcl-S TIME0        Time       INZ(T'10.12.15'); //     130129
0.00    Dcl-S TIME0_CHAR   Char(8); //     130129

        //Into date testing
8.00    DATE0 = *DATE;
9.00    DATE1 = %Date(010112:*MDY);
0.00    DATE2 = %Date('01/01/12':*MDY/);

6.00    ORG=192;
7.00    ACC='A00000000017';
8.00    SETLL (ORG:ACC) ACCOUNT;
9.00    IF %EQUAL(ACCOUNT);
0.00      READ ACCOUNT;
1.00      CCY='AZK';
2.00      EXCEPT UPDATE_R;
3.00    ENDIF;

        //___MAIN SUBROUTINE BEGINGS HERE_______________
0.00    BEGSR MAIN;
8.01      READC EXPD_SFL;
8.02      DOW NOT %EOF();
8.03        SELECT;
8.04          When S_OPT = '1';
8.05            EXSR OPTION1;
8.06          When S_OPT = '2';
8.07            EXSR OPTION2;
0808          When S_OPT = '4';
8.09            EXSR OPTION4;
0.10          When S_OPT = '5';
8.11            EXSR OPTION5;
0.12          OTHER;
0.13            EXSR VALIDATE;
0.14        ENDSL;
0.15        READC EXPD_SFL;
8.16      ENDDO;
8.18      MODE='1';
0.00    ENDSR;

4.00    *InLR = *On;
